  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the READ study is to compare the continuation of the cardiac rehabilitation at
      home with clinical follow-up, therapeutic education, and advice on the training at the
      stamina, via telemedicine with the classic strategy in day hospital.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
